          contemporary art appreciated by 14% annually (1995-2021)
         </em>
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         <em>
          As an asset class, art isn\xe2\x80\x99t a GME or South Sea. You won\xe2\x80\x99t 10x your investment in 24 hours, but you probably won\xe2\x80\x99t lose 90% of it either.
         </em>
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
